---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services | Spectro Elevators - Installation, AMC, Repairs & Modernization" description="Read about our elevator installation process, Annual Maintenance Contracts (AMC), modernizations, and 24x7 emergency rescue service response times in Bihar." activePage="services">
  <!-- Inner Page Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-primary py-24 text-white overflow-hidden pt-36">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504917595217-d4dc5ebe6122?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80" alt="Technical maintenance services" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary via-primary/95 to-primary"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4" data-aos="fade-up">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold font-heading">Our Elevator Services</h1>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-accent mx-auto"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">From initial survey, custom installation blueprints, to monthly maintenance packages and modernization.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Detailed Service Description -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-24">

      <!-- 1. Installation Process -->
      <div id="installation" class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center scroll-mt-36" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="bg-primary text-accent text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded">Service 01</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary font-heading">Elevator Installation Process</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Installing a new elevator is a complex engineering task that requires precise structural alignment. Our installation process is divided into distinct, transparent phases to ensure safety and code compliance.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent text-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0">1</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-primary">Structural Site Survey</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">We measure shaft width, pit depth, overhead clearance, and load capacities of your building's lift column.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent text-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0">2</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-primary">CAD Blueprint Design</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">Engineers generate a custom layout drawing showing bracket points, machine location, and cable pathways.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent text-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0">3</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-primary">Mechanical Assembly & Wiring</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">Anchoring guide rails, hanging traction motors, routing steel cables, and connecting digital control boxes.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-accent text-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0">4</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-primary">Safety Verification Testing</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">A 45-point inspection checklist verifying emergency brakes, ARD power failure rescue, and weight balancing.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-6">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504307651254-35680f356dfd?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Elevator installation shaft work" class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-[400px] object-cover border border-slate-100">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. AMC Packages -->
      <div id="amc" class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center scroll-mt-36" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092160607-ee22621dd758?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Technician checking control panel" class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-[400px] object-cover border border-slate-100">
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-6 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="bg-primary text-accent text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded">Service 02</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary font-heading">Structured AMC Maintenance</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Avoid unexpected breakdowns and prolong your elevator's lifespan with our Annual Maintenance Contracts. We offer monthly diagnostic checks, lubrication, and immediate response dispatch.
          </p>

          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-4">
            <div class="border border-slate-200 p-5 rounded-xl space-y-3 bg-bgTint shadow-sm">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-primary text-base border-b border-slate-200 pb-2">Semi-Comprehensive</h4>
              <ul class="text-xs text-slate-500 space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-accent"></i> 12 Scheduled Monthly Checks</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-accent"></i> 24x7 Breakdown Dispatch</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-accent"></i> Cabin & Pit Cleaning</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="x" class="w-4 h-4 text-rose-500"></i> Spare Parts Charged Extra</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="border-2 border-accent p-5 rounded-xl space-y-3 bg-primary text-white shadow-lg">
              <h4 class="font-bold text-accent text-base border-b border-white/10 pb-2">Comprehensive</h4>
              <ul class="text-xs text-slate-300 space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-accent"></i> All Semi-Comprehensive items</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-accent"></i> FREE Spare Part Replacements</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-accent"></i> Control board, ropes covered</li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><i data-lucide="check" class="w-4 h-4 text-accent"></i> Safety gear replacements</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4">
            <a href="amc.html" class="inline-block bg-accent hover:bg-accentHover text-primary font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-custom text-sm shadow-md">
              Learn More About AMC
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Modernization & Repairs -->
      <div id="modernization" class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center scroll-mt-36" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="bg-primary text-accent text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded">Service 03</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary font-heading">Elevator Modernization & Repairs</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Is your existing elevator over 10 years old? Is it noisy, slow, or constantly breaking down? Our modernization service upgrades your elevator machinery and electronics without requiring complete structural shaft rebuilding.
          </p>
          
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <i data-lucide="check-square" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
              <span><strong>Traction Machine Upgrades:</strong> Replace loud geared machines with whisper-quiet, energy-saving permanent magnet gearless motors.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <i data-lucide="check-square" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
              <span><strong>Microprocessor Controllers:</strong> Upgrade legacy relay cabinets to 32-bit digital loop controllers for faster floor responses.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <i data-lucide="check-square" class="w-5 h-5 text-accent shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
              <span><strong>Cabin Aesthetic Face-lift:</strong> Install modern stainless steel finishes, energy-saving LED panels, and modern buttons.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-6">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517524206127-48bbd363f3d7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Elevator repair work" class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-[400px] object-cover border border-slate-100">
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. Emergency Response & Local Support -->
      <div id="emergency" class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center scroll-mt-36" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden text-center space-y-6">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 safety-stripes opacity-5 -skew-y-6"></div>
            <i data-lucide="phone-call" class="w-16 h-16 text-accent mx-auto animate-bounce"></i>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-heading">24x7 Emergency Line</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">In case of elevator blockages or passenger entrapment, contact our dispatch line immediately.</p>
            <span class="block text-3xl font-extrabold text-accent font-heading">+91 98014 51329</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-6 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="bg-primary text-accent text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded">Service 04</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary font-heading">Emergency Rescue & Dispatch</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Safety is our highest priority. We maintain a fleet of quick-response support vehicles manned by certified technicians and equipped with safety gear to respond to elevator failures.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
              <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-6 h-6 text-accent shrink-0"></i>
              <span><strong>Patna Response Time:</strong> Guaranteed technician onsite under 1 hour.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
              <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-6 h-6 text-accent shrink-0"></i>
              <span><strong>Other Cities (Gaya, Muzaffarpur):</strong> Onsite response under 3 hours.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
              <i data-lucide="users-2" class="w-6 h-6 text-accent shrink-0"></i>
              <span><strong>Support Staff:</strong> Local technicians reside directly inside key district headquarters.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer Section -->
</Layout>
